    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Help resolve a course access issue for this learner:\n\nLearner ID: {{ $(\"Learner Support Form\").item.json.learnerId }}\nEmail: {{ $(\"Learner Support Form\").item.json.email }}\nQuery: {{ $(\"Learner Support Form\").item.json.query }}\n\nSteps:\n1. Use the Google Sheets Tool to look up the learner's account details using their learner ID\n2. Check their enrollment status, course visibility, and account status\n3. Identify if this is a login issue (wrong credentials, password reset) or visibility issue (course not showing)\n4. Look up the relevant FAQ answer from the FAQ_Knowledge_Base sheet\n5. Generate a personalized response that includes:\n   - Acknowledgment of their specific issue\n   - Account-specific context (e.g., \"I can see you're enrolled in...\")\n   - Step-by-step solution from the FAQ\n   - Offer to escalate if the solution doesn't work\n\nBe empathetic, clear, and specific.",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an Access Specialist for CodeBasics. You have access to learner account data via Google Sheets. Use the Google Sheets Tool to retrieve learner information and provide personalized support. Always look up data before responding."
        }
      },
