        "text": "=Generate a refund response based on eligibility:\n\nLearner Email: {{ $(\"Manual Trigger\").item.json.email }}\nEligible: {{ $json.output.eligible }}\nPurchase Date: {{ $json.output.purchaseDate }}\nCompletion: {{ $json.output.completionPercentage }}%\nDays Since Purchase: {{ $json.output.daysSincePurchase }}\n\nIf ELIGIBLE:\n- Confirm refund approval\n- Explain the refund will be processed within 5-7 business days\n- Thank them for trying CodeBasics\n\nIf NOT ELIGIBLE:\n- Politely explain the refund policy (1 day window, ≤20% completion)\n- Show their specific data (purchased X days ago, completed Y%)\n- Offer alternative support (course extension, additional resources)\n- Maintain empathetic and professional tone",
